name: Ce n'est pas un hommage à Magritte
description:
Interactive 3D piece made in the Spline Tool. Move the mouse to interact with the elements of the scene.Use the mouse click to rotate the scene and command + scroll up and down to zoom. SVG format.

* It is recommended to use the Chrome Internet browser for a better visualization of 3D elements. Safari and other browsers do not render 3D elements correctly. Please consider this.

**The piece is not viewed in full screen, please consider this before purchasing. However, you can see the piece in full screen through the following link: https://my.spline.design/ma-204edd42e3af9a70a29ed67eeb73d305/
